QuestData.Title: Back on Track
QuestData.Description: Now that the batteries are out of the bog I can radio in some more copters to take them to camp.$B$BI'll stay here until they arrive, but you should go ahead to my brother Dilbert and let him know what happened. He must be worried sick!
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Dilbert Tinkertoss in Veil Zekk.
